Distribution ( Fig. 133 ). Present in Argentina , Bolivia , Brazil , Colombia , Costa Rica , Ecuador , El Salvador , French Guiana , Guatemala , Guyana , Honduras , Mexico , Nicaragua , Panama , Paraguay , Peru , Trinidad and Tobago , Uruguay , and Venezuela ( Gonzalez & Gonzalez 2009 ; Moure 2012 ). In Mexico present in Oaxaca , and in the majority of Central American countries, in the following ecoregions (
Dinerstein et al . 2017
): Dry forests of Central America, Pine-oak forests of Central America, Dry forests of the Central Depression of Chiapas , Seasonal Humid forests of Costa Rica , Humid isthmus-Atlantic forests, Humid isthmus-Pacific forests, Dry forests of Panama , Humid forests of Petén-Veracruz, Humid forests of the Sierra Madre of Chiapas, Dry forests of the South Pacific and Mountainous Forests Talamanca. Wide altitudinal distribution from 0 to 2180 m .
